Depends: ${misc:Depends}, mpv, yt-dlp
Recommends: ffmpeg
Description: Terminal Music Room — CLI/TUI client
 Synchronized YouTube listening in the terminal with mpv playback.
 Join rooms, chat, vote, and listen in sync with your team.

Package: music-roomd
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, yt-dlp
Recommends: ffmpeg
Description: Terminal Music Room — sync server
 Managed WebSocket hub for room state, authoritative playback,
